# User

This rules describes about **user** entity and it's behaviour

## Entity

### User

- ID: Identity of User - New Identity
- TenantID: Identity of Tenant - constructor input, referenced from internal/domain/tenant. No need to define here
- Email: Email - constructor input
- Name: string - constructor input
- Role: Enumerated string of "admin", "member", default("member") - constructor input
- CipherText: CipherText - Default: "", secret
- Status: Enumerated string of "active", "inactive", default("active")

---

## Validation Rules
- Email must be valid format
- Name is required
- Status must be one of "active" or "inactive"
- Role must be one of "admin" or "member"

## Business Logic
- Only "active" users can log in
- Only "admin" users can manage tenants
- Add allowed status/role transitions here as needed

